vishnesh = int(input())
for vish in range(vishnesh):
    (n, k) = list(map(int, input().split()))
    arr = list(map(int, input().split()))
    s = list(range(1, n + 1))
    for i in range(k):
        s.remove(arr[i])
    if n - k == 0:
        print(-1, end=' ')
    i = 0
    while i < n - k:
        print(s[i], end=' ')
        i = i + 2
    print()
    if n - k < 2:
        print(-1, end=' ')
    i = 1
    while i < n - k:
        print(s[i], end=' ')
        i = i + 2
    print()
